302\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">п. Марія&nbsp; Щербатих, п. Ірина</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"149\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Дошкільнята</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"104\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">11:50 &ndash; 12:20</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\" width=\"180\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">хатинка на алеї, що веде до церкви</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"302\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">п. Світлана Заяць, п. Ореста Цембрівська</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"149\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Дитячий хор</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"104\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">14:00 &ndash; 15:00</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"302\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">п. Руслана Дмитровська</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"149\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Підлітки, молодь</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"104\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">14:00 &ndash; 15:00</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"180\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">крипта</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"302\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Андрій Павлюк</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</t